      "text": "거기에서도 왠지 굉장히 사랑스럽고 발랄한 그런 역할을 맡으셨을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.4,
      "end": 154.54,
      "text": "Yeah, she's a lovely Greek aunt. Full of life and passion. And also the guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.54,
      "end": 163.26,
      "text": "Danny Aiello. Yes. The grandpa. The nano. Danny Aiello. I saw him in The Godfather."
    },
    {
