      "end": 169.32,
      "text": "Danny Aiello. 이런 이름을 가지고 있고. 아, 대부에서 출연이 있었나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.68,
      "end": 176.58,
      "text": "Yes. He did. He was, I think he was a hit man. And he was assassinating someone. And he"
    },
    {
